data.description: An exceptional opportunity awaits! Don't let this one slip by. This beautiful ranch-style home is ideally positioned on a quiet cul-de-sac street with no through traffic, ensuring a peaceful living environment. Set upon a spacious lot that provides a semi-private ambiance, this home features neutral decor that offers a blank canvas for your personal style. With all the living space conveniently situated on a single floor, it's designed for effortless, move-in-ready living. The lower level has been thoughtfully finished, offering a comfortable family room for relaxation, a versatile den, and a functional office space to accommodate your specific needs. This is your chance to embrace the simplicity and comfort of single-floor living in a tranquil and inviting setting. Don't miss this opportunity to make this delightful ranch home your own.
